We stopped in for something light before heading to the ballgame.  (Gotta have room for a hot dog at the ball park).  We split the club sandwich and it was just right.    Service was attentive and the retro decor was welcoming and comfortable.  Nice selection of wines.  I would definitely return if the opportunity came up.

